# 07/01/2025

### User story


1. As a user, I want to be able to repeat my pronunciation mistakes so that I can improve my accent.
2. As a user, I want a button to slow down the audio so I can understand it better.
3. As a user, I want a clear visual cue to help me identify exactly what I’m doing wrong.
4. As a user, I want to be able to repeat my mistakes after every iteration.
5. As a user, I want the information provided on the cards to be simple and clear.
6. As a user, I want to practice by themes or categories.
7. As a user, I want an example or context for any word I’m learning.
8. As a user, I want to see the phonetic transcription of the word so I can pronounce it correctly.
9. As a user, I want to save difficult words or phrases to review them later.
10. As a user, I want to track my progress over time to see how much I’ve improved.
